;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="g2_12" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#ffcc80;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;arcSize=20;" value="Operator-Granted&lt;br&gt;Managed Access&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:8px&quot;&gt;(ADR-031 Proposed · API BUILT&lt;br&gt;— absent from the 07-10 map)&lt;/font&gt;"><mxGeometry height="60" width="190" x="480" y="1180" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_12_0" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;" value="PUT/GET /users/{sub}/entitlement — BUILT + audited"><mxGeometry height="34" width="280" x="140" y="1090" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_12_0" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_12" target="l2_12_0" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#d79b00;strokeWidth=1.5;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_12_1" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;" value="Comped, cost-capped, time-boxed, provider-scoped grants — no payment processor"><mxGeometry height="44" width="280" x="140" y="1128" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_12_1" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_12" target="l2_12_1" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#d79b00;strokeWidth=1.5;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_12_2" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#7f2f2f;fontStyle=1" value="D4 feature entitlements (Plan.features) — NOT BUILT, so EPUB/PDF export stays UNGATED. Admin console UI also missing."><mxGeometry height="54" width="280" x="140" y="1176" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_12_2" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_12" target="l2_12_2" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_12_3" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#1a5c1a;" value="BYOK is the graduation AND the fallback (D6)"><mxGeometry height="24" width="280" x="140" y="1234" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_12_3" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_12" target="l2_12_3" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#82b366;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_12_4" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#7f2f2f;" value="First ADR where the VENDOR carries a token bill. Sybil risk held off only because grants are owner-discretionary (D8)."><mxGeometry height="54" width="280" x="140" y="1262" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_12_4" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_12" target="l2_12_4" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_r12" parent="1" edge="1" source="root2" target="g2_12" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#d79b00;strokeWidth=1.5;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="g2_13" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#7f2f2f;" value="Server-Hosted Library&lt;br&gt;+ Hosted RAG&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:8px&quot;&gt;(ADR-032 Proposed · ZERO CODE)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;THESIS REVERSAL&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;"><mxGeometry height="70" width="190" x="480" y="1520" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_13_0" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#7f2f2f;fontStyle=1" value="AMENDS ADR-001 — hosted RAG runs on MANAGED keys, never the user's. The BYOK moat is the thing being traded."><mxGeometry height="54" width="280" x="140" y="1400" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_13_0" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="l2_13_0" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_13_1" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#7f2f2f;" value="&quot;A reversal of ADR-028's core promise&quot; — its own words. Also amends ADR-014 D8 (device-local default)."><mxGeometry height="54" width="280" x="140" y="1458" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_13_1" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="l2_13_1" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_13_2" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#1a5c1a;" value="D11-D14 (good): PD-only corpus, shared + deduped, server fetches from the vetted source — never accepts client bytes (anti-poisoning)"><mxGeometry height="54" width="280" x="140" y="1516" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_13_2" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="l2_13_2" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#82b366;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_13_3" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#7f2f2f;fontStyle=1" value="D15: free-tier grounding is NOT gated on billing — the vendor pays tokens for users who pay nothing. The ADR concedes this &quot;breaks D10's abuse argument&quot;, then names no limits."><mxGeometry height="64" width="280" x="140" y="1574" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_13_3" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="l2_13_3" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_13_4" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#1a5c1a;" value="Paid hosted tier — gated on the managed-billing launch (D9)"><mxGeometry height="34" width="280" x="140" y="1644" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_13_4" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="l2_13_4" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#82b366;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="l2_13_5" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;arcSize=20;dashed=1;fontColor=#7f2f2f;" value="OPEN: OQ-A1 — do the user's own manuscripts go server-side? (&quot;cannot be zero-knowledge&quot;) · OQ-A4 — what does the paid tier still sell?"><mxGeometry height="64" width="280" x="140" y="1682" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_gg2_13_5" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="l2_13_5" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="e2_r13" parent="1" edge="1" source="root2" target="g2_13" style="edgeStyle=entityRelationEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=none;rounded=0;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_0" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_9" target="l2_6_3" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_2" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_10" target="g2_0" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_4" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_10" target="l2_4_0" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_5" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_11" target="l2_4_3" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_6" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_11" target="l2_1_3" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_9" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_12" target="l2_1_2" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_10" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_12" target="l2_1_3" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_11" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="g2_1" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;" value="amends ADR-001"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_12" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="g2_9" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;" value="reverses D2/D3/D6"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_13" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="g2_10" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;" value="reshapes"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_14" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="g2_11" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;" value="reshapes"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="imp_15" parent="1" edge="1" source="g2_13" target="g2_12" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=block;endFill=1;rounded=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;strokeWidth=1.2;dashed=1;" value="reuses Plan/entitlement"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="risk" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;arcSize=8;fontColor=#7f2f2f;" value="&lt;b&gt;P0 — open, verified on disk 2026-07-14&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. CORS is still allow_origins=[&quot;*&quot;]&lt;/b&gt; (backend/main.py:80) on a &lt;b&gt;LIVE prod backend&lt;/b&gt; whose request bodies carry the user's BYOK key. The critique excused this &quot;before any public URL&quot; — &lt;i&gt;the public URL now exists.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. managed_account_spend_ceiling_micros = 0&lt;/b&gt; ⇒ no ceiling. ADR-031 D3/D8, ADR-032 D10 &lt;i&gt;and&lt;/i&gt; D15 each cite this ceiling as the control that bounds abuse. Harmless only because managed_plan_emails is empty — the day it isn't, three ADRs' safety arguments go vacuous at once.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. In-app help promises starter libraries that do not exist&lt;/b&gt; (help-content/topics.ts:319). A user-visible false claim, shipping in production today."><mxGeometry height="260" width="330" x="690" y="1000" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="foot" parent="1" vertex="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontColor=#666666;" value="LEGEND — ORANGE solid = built and live · orange dashed/grey = built-but-off or partial · GREEN dashed = proposed, ZERO code on disk · RED = aspirational (claimed but not built), or an open P0 risk · purple dashed arrow = impact/dependency · red arrow = amends or reverses a previously-accepted ADR.&#10;&#10;METHOD — every node was checked by grep against source at main@28a62c8 (677 commits, 2026-07-14), NOT by reading the ADRs. Open Shelves is ~83% BUILT (backend/src/shelves 271 LOC + 30 tests; mobile/src/openshelves 17 modules) though ADR-028 is still marked Proposed. ADR-029/030/032 have ZERO implementation. ADR-031's grant API is built and audited, but its one net-new axis (Plan.features) does not exist. Three nodes on the 2026-07-10 map turned out to be aspirational: quiz generation, versioned BookTemplates, and the OPDS starter feeds.&#10;&#10;BUILD ORDER — everything hosted is gated on the managed-billing launch (ADR-032 D9) EXCEPT free-tier grounding (D15), which is deliberately un-gated. That single un-gated edge is the one carrying new token liability."><mxGeometry height="140" width="1400" x="40" y="1770" as="geometry" /></mxCell></root></mxGraphModel></diagram></mxfile>
